text: William Norman Barton III is an American professional basketball player for the Denver Nuggets of the National Basketball Association. He played college basketball for Memphis, where he won the Conference USA Player of the Year in 2012.
Denver Nuggets (#5 / Small forward, Shooting guard)
University of Memphis (2010–2012), Brewster Academy, Lake Clifton High School
